Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:17.11,Title1,,0,0,0,,{\bord4.5\blur2.5\pos(960,800)\3c&HFFFFFF&}家有女友
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.05,0:26:09.57,Sub-CN,,0,0,0,,对不起啦 我爱你
